Package com.pandora.calculation.repositories

Interface FixCellDataRepository

All Known Implementing Classes:
FixCellDataRepositoryImpl
public interface FixCellDataRepository
An interface representing a repository for storing FixCellDataPoint objects. Implementations of this interface are responsible for saving and retrieving FixCellDataPoint objects.
